item.title: P and VPs
item.description: The President and Vice Presidents are responsible for leading the normal operations of the committee. They oversee respective departments to ensure that activities and events were planned and executed in a timely manner. They chair meetings and make critical decisions to ensure that the goals of the management committee are achieved.

item.title: Admin
